    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously have to see this beauty in person to believe it! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in such incredible shape it basically looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been totally babied since day one\u2014spotless inside and out, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels and smells brand new, this is the one for you! Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
      "price": 43800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
