    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving naturally aspirated performance. At its heart lies the S65 4.0L V8, featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS, delivering a visceral 8,400 RPM redline. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with documented preventative rod bearing and throttle actuator replacements. The 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission provides lightning-quick shifts, paired with a perfectly calibrated M-Variable Differential Lock. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), offering precise handling dynamics. The exterior retains its factory-correct finish with no discernible imperfections, while the interior and undercarriage reflect a life of climate-controlled storage and rigorous maintenance.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Full service history. No accidents. Garage kept.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
