    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m so excited to find a new home for this absolute beauty! Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that you\u2019d swear it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one\u2014not a single scratch on it and it still has that fresh, new-car feel. It drives like a total dream! You really have to see it in person to believe how pristine it is. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel today!",
      "price": 43500.0,
