    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an impeccable 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather. This example features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver 333hp at a 7,900 RPM redline. Mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain is flawless. This chassis has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement, a full VANOS overhaul, and structural subframe reinforcement. The suspension retains its factory-correct geometry with fresh bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the telepathic turn-in these cars are known for. Zero deferred maintenance; a true turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
